premise_source_doc_sentence: Allison Beth Adler  (  born May 30 , 1967  )  is an American television producer and writer .
She is best known as the co-creator of Supergirl , The New Normal and her work on Chuck and Family Guy .
Brixius is engaged to producer Allison Adler .
`` Brian Wallows and Peter 's Swallows '' was written by Allison Adler and directed by Dan Povenmire .
Platystomatichthys sturio is the only species in the genus Platystomatichthys of the catfish  (  order Siluriformes  )  family Pimelodidae .
Platystomatichthys is classified under the `` Calophysus-Pimelodus clade '' .

The only Gemini spacecraft not on a Titan II was the re-flight of Gemini 2 for a Manned Orbiting Laboratory test in 1966 , which used a Titan IIIC Gemini was the first program to use the newly built Mission Control Center at the Houston Manned Spacecraft Center for flight control.Gemini 3 used the Mercury Control Center located at Cape Kennedy for flight control , as the new center was still in a test status .
